column5: Nice to see some board members today  ...what wasn't nice was watching you going fishing ...glad you guys all caught fish see ya again soon.. ;D  Wildthing  on the walk back â€¦sorry kevin for no pic but im sure you have some ..  Fishlips  what times lunch ..  Sorry never caught your board name guy ..you did very well for the 1st trip out ..  The river is good to fish now with 5" of ice on 90% of the river ...buck shots tipped with minnows has been  the ticket in 13 fow ..little up river from Vic Powells
Nice fishin guys !!! great report & pics too.... perfect sized eaters....cheers
Awesome Steve, thanks for the report. Hopefully I'll be out that way & see ya Sunday.
Awesome! Glad to see there is ice there again!
I can't wait to get my first hardwater walleye,,i'll be down this week for sure!
